findMatches

public int findMatches(Document doc,
                       FmtLayout layout,
                       FmtPattern acCreator,
                       java.util.List<AC> affectedACs,
                       java.util.List<AC> newACs)
Finds matches of layout formatting pattern given by layout in document.

Parameters:
doc - Document to analyze
layout - Format layout to be found in doc
acCreator - If null, the method only counts matches. Otherwise, new ACs are created and old ones are updated.
affectedACs - array to be filled with all ACs whose score changed
newACs - array to be filled with all newly induced ACs
Returns:
number of matches in doc.
